      • nativeLibraryDeliver

        @Nullable
public byte[] nativeLibraryDeliver​(String query)
                            throws RemoteException
        The query string is the name of a native library to serve back. The requesting place is searching for a native library (.so or .dll) to use. If we have what the requestor is looking for in our libraryDirectory, serve it back to them as an array of bytes.
        Throws:
        RemoteException
